Introduction

Boeun is a South Korean singer under M25.

On September 8, 2021, Boeun was revealed as a contestant on the MBC's survival show "My Teenage Girl". During the finale, she ranked sixth place with 201,684.4 votes, thus becoming a member of the girl group CLASS:y. CLASS:y made their debut on May 5, 2022 with the mini album "Class Is Over".

On January 14, 2024, Boeun was reported as one of the member of PocketDol Studio's collaboration group, A SIX. They released the digital single "Lies All Love" on January 30, 2024.
